Description:
To support our company growth plans, we're seeking a Junior Data Engineer to develop, maintain and improve our existing data engineering lifecycle. This will cover the whole data journey from the ETL process to providing critical insights to clients. Your role will work closely with the Head of Data, Team Leads, and internal/external stakeholders.
As a company, we recognise that our business value comes from our exceptional people. We have a growth mindset, are ambitious, and love seeing the impact of our work on our clients' success. We deliver data-driven insights to help our clients develop informed and effective strategies to reach their desired outcomes. We are flexible, and we work openly. We offer tailored solutions to our clients and can readily switch course when needed. We value the work we do and the relationships we build, making them meaningful beyond the day-to-day.
